          It's just...          
      I got some bad news.      

02:30.400 --> 02:33.600
You guys all remember the       
Miss Boston Barmaid contest?    

02:33.700 --> 02:35.000
      Oh, yeah.                 

02:35.100 --> 02:36.000
    That's the annual contest   

02:36.000 --> 02:37.600
            where they try to   
          find the most talented

02:37.700 --> 02:39.200
                and efficient   
             waitress in Boston,

02:39.300 --> 02:40.800
            which-- surprise,   
                surprise--      

