 always turns out to be the babe
     with the biggest honeydews.

02:45.500 --> 02:48.300
     Right. Well, this year     
 they're holding it at Cheers.  

02:48.300 --> 02:49.700
         All right!             
  All right!                    

02:49.800 --> 02:51.100
      No, no, no, no. No,       
