Thank you, Woody.               
                      You should

04:03.000 --> 04:03.700
do it, Carla.                   

04:03.700 --> 04:04.500
                Look, I know    

04:04.600 --> 04:05.600
        I'm a good waitress.    

04:05.700 --> 04:07.100
            I don't need        
        some obnoxious dork     

04:07.200 --> 04:09.000
            in a cheap suit     
        telling me I'm the best.

04:09.100 --> 04:10.000
But you <i>are</i> the best.           

04:10.100 --> 04:11.800
                I just said I   
            didn't need that.   

04:14.400 --> 04:16.800
  Besides, even if I did win,   
    what would I get?           

04:16.800 --> 04:18.899
A lousy ten bucks               
and a handshake?                
                        Well,   

04:19.000 --> 04:21.100
      it says here you get      
    a brand new Mazda Miata.    

04:21.200 --> 04:24.200
    Get out of town.            

04:24.200 --> 04:25.800
Just for doing my job?          

04:25.900 --> 04:27.500
                         Mm-hmm.

04:27.600 --> 04:29.900
        Oh...                   

04:29.900 --> 04:31.400
I'm gonna get myself this Miata.

04:31.500 --> 04:32.500
                      All right.

04:32.600 --> 04:33.500
Yeah.                           

04:33.600 --> 04:35.700
                Uh! Uh-oh. Snag.

04:35.800 --> 04:38.400
             What about warmth, 
             personal courtesy? 

04:40.900 --> 04:43.600
What about me shoving this      
  brochure up your nose?        

