  Oh, it's worth it.            

08:19.700 --> 08:21.100
It's worth it.                  
                    Yeah.       

08:21.100 --> 08:22.800
      Carla, this must've       
fallen out of your folder.      

08:22.800 --> 08:24.300
It says "List of Judges."       

08:25.700 --> 08:27.000
    Are you kidding?            

08:27.100 --> 08:30.000
  That's supposed               
  to be top secret.             

08:30.000 --> 08:31.300
Oh, my God.                     

08:31.400 --> 08:33.900
This is the best thing          
that's ever happened to me.     

08:34.000 --> 08:35.100
I'm gonna know who they are.    

08:35.200 --> 08:37.600
Now all I have to do is         
kiss up to the squids           

08:37.700 --> 08:39.200
on that list and I'll           
be driving home                 

08:39.299 --> 08:40.500
in a nice, new convertible.     

08:40.500 --> 08:41.799
                    All right.  

08:41.900 --> 08:43.200
Who are they, Woody?            

08:43.200 --> 08:45.500
David Murphy, Cliff Clavin      

08:45.600 --> 08:46.800
and Frank Smith.                

08:48.600 --> 08:50.500
     (yells)                    

08:57.500 --> 08:59.500
Now, who is Frank Smith,        

08:59.600 --> 09:01.500
and why is Carla so mad at him? 

09:10.200 --> 09:12.900
                 And now, on top
             of everything else,

09:13.000 --> 09:15.800
              I've got this huge
         headache outta nowhere.

09:18.500 --> 09:20.800
              They picked Clavin
                to be a judge.  

09:20.900 --> 09:22.800
                 What could they
          have been thinking of?

09:24.500 --> 09:25.900
    Aw, they probably           
    want someone, you know,     

09:26.000 --> 09:27.200
  with lot of bar experience,   

09:27.300 --> 09:29.500
and he <i>has</i> been hanging         
around here a lot, you know.    

09:29.500 --> 09:30.600
     Yeah, well, so's Norm.     

09:30.600 --> 09:31.900
Why didn't they pick you, Norm? 

09:32.000 --> 09:32.900
     Well, maybe they did.      

09:33.000 --> 09:35.800
