09:43.500 --> 09:47.100
                  when they were
            just bimbo contests.

09:47.200 --> 09:48.500
            You know, if this...

09:48.600 --> 09:50.800
             this is the new age
            of enlightenment,   

09:50.900 --> 09:53.200
