10:00.700 --> 10:01.900
     All right.                 

10:01.900 --> 10:03.100
    You know, over the years,   

10:03.200 --> 10:05.300
            I've been pretty    
                bad to Clavin.  
    Mmm.                        

10:05.400 --> 10:06.700
            And I've done       
             some things that...

10:06.800 --> 10:08.500
         maybe I shouldn't have.

10:08.600 --> 10:10.500
     Mm-hmm.                    
            Called him names.   

10:10.600 --> 10:12.500
            Punctured his tires.

10:12.600 --> 10:14.100
        Set fire to his hair.   

10:14.200 --> 10:16.400
    What's the question?        

10:16.500 --> 10:17.500
        Do you think he noticed?

10:17.600 --> 10:18.900
    (snorts)                    

10:19.000 --> 10:22.000
You made this guy               
    eat a bug once.             

10:22.100 --> 10:25.500
Come on, that's a birthday      
the guy's never gonna forget.   

10:25.600 --> 10:27.600
                 Okay, I'll send
                him flowers.    

10:27.600 --> 10:30.200
Carla, that bug laid            
eggs in his stomach.            

10:31.900 --> 10:34.000
                Yeah. That <i>was</i>  
                kind of a bonus.

10:35.600 --> 10:37.000
                Oh... God.      

10:37.100 --> 10:39.300
            I might as well just
            chop this phony bow.

10:39.400 --> 10:40.500
              Aww.              

10:40.600 --> 10:42.500
You're right, Norm.             
      It's hopeless.            

10:42.600 --> 10:43.700
I'm never gonna win anything.   

10:43.800 --> 10:45.200
                  Come on.      
    No, really.                 

10:45.300 --> 10:47.200
  You know, I thought           
    it was my turn.             

10:47.300 --> 10:49.200
  I thought that,               
for once in my life,            

10:49.300 --> 10:50.500
I was gonna be recognized       

10:50.600 --> 10:52.900
for being the best              
  at what I do.                 

10:52.900 --> 10:55.700
Now, because of Clavin,         
I don't even get the chance.    

10:55.800 --> 10:58.600
            All right, well, why
             don't you try this?

10:58.600 --> 11:00.400
      Actually be nice to Cliff.

11:00.500 --> 11:02.200
          Listen to his stories.

11:02.300 --> 11:04.200
        Treat him like a friend.

11:04.300 --> 11:05.500
                (laughs):       
                I'm sorry.      

11:05.500 --> 11:08.500
