     You all right, Carla?      

11:32.600 --> 11:33.800
  Beat it, lard butt!           

11:35.900 --> 11:38.100
      Thank God. I thought      
      I was hallucinating.      

11:41.100 --> 11:42.000
                Interested, huh?

11:42.100 --> 11:43.400
Oh, yeah!                       
                That's funny.   

11:43.400 --> 11:45.500
              You, uh, you never
          listened to me before.

11:45.500 --> 11:48.200
        I listen to you         
      all the time, Cliff.      

11:48.300 --> 11:50.100
Yeah, as a matter of fact,      

11:50.100 --> 11:52.600
        I often go home         
    and tell the kids           

11:52.600 --> 11:55.500
        about this very,        
    very smart man at work.     

11:55.600 --> 11:58.200
      Why are you so mean       
      to me all the time?       

11:58.300 --> 11:59.900
             Mean?              

12:00.000 --> 12:03.700
 Well, like when you knocked me 
        off that stool.         

12:03.700 --> 12:06.300
    Knocked... Oh, no!          

12:06.400 --> 12:08.400
     Oh, no, that was just      
     an affectionate nudge,     

12:08.500 --> 12:12.200
you, you old silly billy.       

12:20.700 --> 12:23.500
    Well, that, that did sort   
                 of hurt my back

12:23.600 --> 12:24.900
                a little bit.   
        Oh...                   

12:25.000 --> 12:29.100
     You know, I wondered if you
    might... Uh, no, never mind.

12:29.100 --> 12:30.200
          I could never ask you.

